[SPEAKER_15]: Tim Alexander from Mill Creek.

45
00:03:43,344 --> 00:03:58,861
[SPEAKER_15]: That is the agenda, so I think a review of the conditions as drafted, and maybe even as proposed revision, and then an update on the linkage waiver as well.

46
00:03:58,981 --> 00:04:04,047
[SPEAKER_15]: I think it might be helpful, and Chris Rainier, if you don't mind, I think it might be helpful for the board to hear

47
00:04:04,903 --> 00:04:16,050
