00:04:24,875 --> 00:04:27,597
[SPEAKER_03]: The board did receive those documents so we can discuss.

51
00:04:31,860 --> 00:04:37,005
[SPEAKER_03]: And then the matter in terms of whether or not to close the hearing, should we just do that at the end?

52
00:04:38,206 --> 00:04:39,847
[SPEAKER_03]: Or is that something we should discuss up front?

53
