00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:44,542
[SPEAKER_15]: Thank you, Mr. Chair.

67
00:05:44,562 --> 00:05:52,528
[SPEAKER_15]: So I think the waivers and the linkage waiver in specific, which was the topic of discussion

