[SPEAKER_15]: Okay, excellent.

80
00:07:42,528 --> 00:07:48,090
[SPEAKER_15]: Yeah, I think a combination, I mean, might be best if Mr. Rainier walks through.

81
00:07:48,110 --> 00:08:07,055
[SPEAKER_15]: We worked on it actually with Louise Gianakis as well, but I think, Chris, you might be the best person to walk the board through the proposed revisions, you know, where they're substantive, where they're simplifications, or where they're maybe just, you know, sort of language

