00:38:00,683 --> 00:38:01,624
[SPEAKER_12]: I'm sorry, you go.

351
00:38:02,584 --> 00:38:28,912
[SPEAKER_03]: Yeah, I was just gonna say to that point, I'm wondering, so as I understand it, so say we were to either not address it at all in the decision or put in language asserting that use is permitted by requiring a special permit or not allowed and would basically require going back

