[SPEAKER_15]: I think it sounds like the board and the applicant are on the same page, right?

405
00:43:38,436 --> 00:43:46,021
[SPEAKER_15]: We know we want a complimentary use that serves both the community we're going to build plus the broader neighborhood.

406
00:43:46,461 --> 00:43:48,202
[SPEAKER_15]: We don't want nuisance type uses.

407
00:43:48,682 --> 00:43:54,486
[SPEAKER_15]: And I think to Chris's point, there are specific use types within the ordinance we can add to the waiver list.

408
