00:44:05,140 --> 00:44:07,643
[SPEAKER_15]: commercial kitchen, that type of infrastructure.

410
00:44:07,663 --> 00:44:21,802
[SPEAKER_15]: And I think just on the third thing on top of that is the fact that we're talking about 2000 square feet, which, you know, is enough to have one to two good sized users, but not enough to, you know, really

411
