[SPEAKER_15]: open up the user pool to a lot of the other types that we might not want.

412
00:44:27,805 --> 00:44:42,740
[SPEAKER_15]: I think a combination of the waiver language, the conditions as drafted, and just the size and design, or lack thereof design, within the approved plans, capital A, capital P, should get us to the right spot.

