01:18:00,005 --> 01:18:01,886
[SPEAKER_14]: vehicular exhausts and things of that nature.

742
01:18:01,946 --> 01:18:07,888
[SPEAKER_14]: So we want our landscaping to be as healthy and thrive as best possible.

743
01:18:07,948 --> 01:18:13,650
[SPEAKER_14]: And so this is language that Rob Adams suggested that we insert to give him that optionality.

744
01:18:16,231 --> 01:18:20,252
