844
01:30:26,705 --> 01:30:35,414
[SPEAKER_15]: is that the mechanical electrical plumbing world is working hard to adjust and really clarify what this means.

845
01:30:36,035 --> 01:30:42,642
[SPEAKER_15]: And I think because of that, there are going to be some changes to the technology that are coming forth that we just may not know about yet.

846
01:30:43,703 --> 01:30:45,165
[SPEAKER_15]: And so I just think that, you know,

847
01:30:46,135 --> 01:30:52,657
[SPEAKER_15]: Having the flexibility to be code compliant is probably important to us, as the code is changing pretty fast.

848
01:30:52,677 --> 01:31:00,140
[SPEAKER_15]: And I know that the real practical world, the design world and the construction world, is working hard to keep up.

849
01:31:01,940 --> 01:31:02,180
[SPEAKER_03]: OK.

850
01:31:02,901 --> 01:31:03,321
[SPEAKER_03]: Thank you.

