02:43:05,550 --> 02:43:05,931
[SPEAKER_03]: Jamie.

1465
02:43:05,951 --> 02:43:09,013
[SPEAKER_03]: Hi, Mike.

1466
02:43:09,193 --> 02:43:09,514
[SPEAKER_03]: Yes.

1467
02:43:09,674 --> 02:43:09,874
[SPEAKER_03]: All right.

1468
02:43:09,894 --> 02:43:17,600
[SPEAKER_03]: We're in recess for, uh, we'll reconvene at 10 35, uh, Alicia, Judy, you have my number if you want to chat.

