[SPEAKER_12]: All right, so we are back in session.

1475
02:43:49,737 --> 02:43:52,499
[SPEAKER_12]: All right, so what are we thinking folks?

1476
02:43:53,119 --> 02:43:53,519
[SPEAKER_12]: Mr. Alexander?

1477
